== Extra Magic Ours

This site is to gather ideas and suggestions for improving the Disney theme parks. By utilizing the community to collaborate on different ideas, and vote up the best ones, hopefully we can make the DIsney theme parks an even more magical place for everyone, where the extra magic is ours.


== Gems

=== jquery-rails
keeps jquery up to date

=== make_voteable
installed, but ditched in favor of thumbs-up

=== thumbs_up
Keeps track of upvoting and downvoting
Has a robust vote filter (can be used to devise a "Hot Topic" based on recent votes)

https://github.com/brady8/thumbs_up

=== omniauth
Used to authorize users

=== devise
Used to authorize users

=== nifty-generators

=== acts-as-taggable-on
https://github.com/mbleigh/acts-as-taggable-on

=== fb_graph
Accesses the facebook GraphAPI
https://github.com/nov/fb_graph

=== acts_as_commentable_with_threading
https://github.com/elight/acts_as_commentable_with_threading
Threads used for further info:
http://stackoverflow.com/questions/2917444/how-to-use-acts-as-commentable-with-threading-in-rails
http://stackoverflow.com/questions/463936/reddit-style-nested-threaded-indented-comments-for-rails
http://stackoverflow.com/questions/4892305/rails-3-acts-as-commentable-with-threading-gem

=== paperclip
Not installed yet, will be used.
https://github.com/thoughtbot/paperclip

